{"tid":421801,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［JJ插雪］北海道10日9夜行程問題","createTime":"2017-10-02T14:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T03:22:45.000Z","uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"20d89816c0ac2727f4fdf581220e9e82a3b42f3b","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚟緊年底會去北海道雙人遊（非自駕），但係由於對北海道唔熟既關係，行程上唔知Plan得有無問題（景點位置順序）<br />\n<br />\n本來想去埋網走，稚內，但發現去埋就無時間去Tamamu滑雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外旭川真係完全唔識Plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左個旭山動物園其他都無乜吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個雪之美術館同旭山動物園仲要打對角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程如下：<br />\n東京》札幌（中午抵達） - 酒店check in》北海道大學》札幌時計塔&amp;電視塔》大通公園》狸小路》薄野 - day1 完<br />\n<br />\n札幌》二條市場》白之戀人公園》北海道神宮》Maruyama Class》札幌髮型屋》札幌啤酒園（成吉思汗羊肉）- day2 完<br />\n*買明天開始的7天jr pass<br />\n<br />\n札幌酒店check out》函館 *0600-0927班次 》函館朝市》酒店check in》金森紅磚倉庫&amp;西波止場》小丑漢堡》函館山夜景》函館元町&amp;灣岸區 - day3 完<br />\n*買函館一日乘車卷<br />\n<br />\n函館酒店check out》函館朝市》函館》登別 *1048-1327班次》溫泉旅館check in 》地獄谷》大湯沼》旅館晚餐》溫泉街》旅館浸溫泉 - day4 完<br />\n<br />\n溫泉旅館check out *行李暫存》熊牧場》伊達時代村》登別》小樽 *1730-1934班次》入住民宿》運河食堂》出拔小路》夜遊運河 - day5 完<br />\n<br />\n酒店check out》小樽 *行李放locker〉南小樽》小樽八音盒堂》商店街》北一硝子》小樽博物館》小樽》旭川 *1710-1925班次》入住民宿》平和通買物公園 - day 6 完<br />\n<br />\n酒店check out》旭川 *行李放locker》旭山動物園》拉麵村》旭川》札幌 *1700-1825班次》激安之殿堂》味覺圓 - day 7 完<br />\n<br />\n札幌》Tamamu渡假村》滑雪 - day 8 完<br />\n<br />\nTamamu渡假村》滑雪 - day 9 完<br />\n<br />\nTamamu渡假村》札幌》東京 - day 10 完<br />\n<br />\n大致Plan完係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有無更好既行程建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccb3733615eefb1b734dfaa8f3c2b239679cd3e","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca247ea67c2ca69ac80c2c55ec8da99a44a20b42","tid":421801,"uid":118976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"day 1未必去到北大睇<br />\nday 5趕去小樽?<br />\n<br />\n冬天北海道4、5點天黑<br />\n另外一遇大風雪,鐵路都可能delay幾個鐘"},{"pid":"eaa94cb3e90e22e17a7440e96decc812d4cbbab6","tid":421801,"uid":33727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"機票買晒未?"},{"pid":"b50a234d2f5def667f7365bc2029bba446bd5cdb","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>day 1未必去到北大睇<br />\nday 5趕去小樽?<br />\n<br />\n冬天北海道4、5點天黑<br />\n另外一遇大風雪,鐵路都可能delay幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\nSorry可能我講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> day5係預朝早加下午玩哂熊牧場同時代村，玩完就會過小樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係確實5點半先過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bf0a1609b2992c8317432a16f9256e0e8f9f11","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機票買晒未?</blockquote><br />\n已經買哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋登別果日既溫泉旅館都訂左，除此之外所有野都未定實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc074d4a56e2f5dfeb3bba5f68e67c8963a4e597","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>day 1未必去到北大睇<br />\nday 5趕去小樽?<br />\n<br />\n冬天北海道4、5點天黑<br />\n另外一遇大風雪,鐵路都可能delay幾個鐘</blockquote><br />\n北大如果去唔到我可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都驚有大風雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075edcf3b9030d23f360c9dda45e957d99a32ca6","tid":421801,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得你無一日嘅行程係可以完成到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ac4ad0577b38829e559660eae35be7d47fad71","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得你無一日嘅行程係可以完成到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a3dd894ac188d6c6c1fe1e9bee9b98ea279c6d","tid":421801,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"第一日都有D忟水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113037ab0cbc1fbf7fc11c9cb91d677388cc3d48","tid":421801,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機票買晒未?</blockquote><br />\n已經買哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋登別果日既溫泉旅館都訂左，除此之外所有野都未定實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲諗住叫你改函館入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到你要搭0600火車就好頭痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb16e5d822d2670fa7d9a6201fbe1360ddd1c2f","tid":421801,"uid":38351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"滑雪book咗酒店未？<br />\n如果未，札幌，二世古，小樽過少少嘅kiroro,富良野都有滑雪場。可以俾自己更多選擇。<br />\n若果真係揀tomamu, 位置近帶廣十勝。建議抽最少一日去行吓，至少浸出名嘅十勝川美人湯。<br />\n如果我係你，排行程如下:<br />\nday 1: 東京- 札幌<br />\nday 2: 札幌- 小樽，即晚返札幌，夜晚薄野食飯，住札幌<br />\nday 3: 札幌朝早行北大/ 中島公園，舊道廳，中午坐酒店巴士去登別。晚飯後行地獄谷，住登別<br />\nday 4: 朝早行大沼/ 忍者村。巴士去函館。黃昏在教堂群散步，夜晚上函館山睇夜景，屋台街晚飯，住湯之川溫泉。<br />\nday 5: 修道院買手工曲奇食雪糕，坐巴士/ 電車到五稜廓觀景塔。自由市場lunch, 谷地頭浸浴，立待岬，函館朝市( 見識) + 金森倉庫群。晚飯後通宵巴士返札幌<br />\nday 6-7 : 札幌滑雪場( 或二世古滑雪)"},{"pid":"f3f099efc0502505e840015818532b23bc113e80","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>機票買晒未?</blockquote><br />\n已經買哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋登別果日既溫泉旅館都訂左，除此之外所有野都未定實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲諗住叫你改函館入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到你要搭0600火車就好頭痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個都唔係大問題嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為之前去東京都試過唔訓直踩玩兩日，今次搭車有得訓下應該會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw多謝巴打你先"},{"pid":"9ccd3f631a4ad1b0b73c45090e9a559107f532f9","tid":421801,"uid":149194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>滑雪book咗酒店未？<br />\n如果未，札幌，二世古，小樽過少少嘅kiroro,富良野都有滑雪場。可以俾自己更多選擇。<br />\n若果真係揀tomamu, 位置近帶廣十勝。建議抽最少一日去行吓，至少浸出名嘅十勝川美人湯。<br />\n如果我係你，排行程如下:<br />\nday 1: 東京- 札幌<br />\nday 2: 札幌- 小樽，即晚返札幌，夜晚薄野食飯，住札幌<br />\nday 3: 札幌朝早行北大/ 中島公園，舊道廳，中午坐酒店巴士去登別。晚飯後行地獄谷，住登別<br />\nday 4: 朝早行大沼/ 忍者村。巴士去函館。黃昏在教堂群散步，夜晚上函館山睇夜景，屋台街晚飯，住湯之川溫泉。<br />\nday 5: 修道院買手工曲奇食雪糕，坐巴士/ 電車到五稜廓觀景塔。自由市場lunch, 谷地頭浸浴，立待岬，函館朝市( 見識) + 金森倉庫群。晚飯後通宵巴士返札幌<br />\nday 6-7 : 札幌滑雪場( 或二世古滑雪)</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打你即刻度出嚟嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好勁好實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw見到你打Tomamu先醒起我打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a26906ed0e22d747a7e30b657eb705957d462bf","tid":421801,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":