/>\n咁登別我行左溫泉街先，夜晚再行地獄谷會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁函館等我食完早餐就去左五棱郭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n夜晚行地獄谷都唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係登別 我夜晚唔會出去玩 一來凍撚死 二來乜都睇唔到 所以建議你逼埋係食飯前好d"},{"pid":"fc2be412a63da66704b49da047d69216cbb00478","tid":421801,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:42:38.000Z","msg":"我去八日 行程唔夠你四日咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862db944ee1fd97f4c886643b16a2d3d661d1479","tid":421801,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:45:28.000Z","msg":"好chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddbba7a678d6460da5a7019c901ada45feff41e","tid":421801,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"我去十日 唔夠你三成景點"},{"pid":"982da7109e155116f6965e7457ff03948a7a5d4b","tid":421801,"uid":39084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去十日 唔夠你三成景點</blockquote><br />\n我去六日自駕都係去左富良野、旭川同小樽。樓主咁玩法應該大部分時間係度坐車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c364124fde4cb94a6dbba0918e87a0e30e3c420","tid":421801,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去十日 唔夠你三成景點</blockquote><br />\n我去六日自駕都係去左富良野、旭川同小樽。樓主咁玩法應該大部分時間係度坐車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 但玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51a24d00af808f9e7040baddecdaf5f9b6fbd34","tid":421801,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小樽可以去出拔小路食天丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我記得間野都好似幾早收舖架</blockquote><br />\n連登仔成日吹奏拔小路，攪到勁多香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n𠴱度不嬲都多港人啦，呢估真係靠連登仔吹奏咩。"},{"pid":"ccfdbda3062c5e5efaac47628d7843b3ca3507b3","tid":421801,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我個次冬天傍晚去溫泉街 啲野好多都關門 晚飯之後去可能更加無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋佢賣個啲野好多係旅館入面嘅手信店都有 <br />\n<br />\n你睇下函館第一日朝早啲時間可唔可以去五棱郭 之後先過倉庫個邊 個人覺得五棱郭有特色d 倉庫周圍都有</blockquote><br />\n咁登別我行左溫泉街先，夜晚再行地獄谷會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁函館等我食完早餐就去左五棱郭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會夜晚走去地獄谷咖，你不如諗諗自已夜晚會唔會走去行郊野公園？向札幌除左市區外其它地方入夜後基本上係人影都冇個。"},{"pid":"c5ceb4d09bf39bdc44c831456a8ea593a72c4ae0","tid":421801,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主飛東京再飛札幌？<br />\n點解既，平啲？ <br />\n飛札幌幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係平過直飛嘅掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我搭香草去無得直飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，你要玩轉機點解唔向東京飛函館順路玩上去而要向札幌落咁戇鳩先？比我係你我就坐 red eyes 飛羽田再轉最早一班機落函館，去到函館分分鐘仲係早上。"},{"pid":"f82a5d09f40ea612e6b1d663bcd6e1e8f39f79f7","tid":421801,"uid":80512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會去函館點解唔搭新幹線要搭內陸機去札幌再搭落去咁晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為搭去函館去札幌都係要咁多時間嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非唔去札幌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉你鐘意啦<br />\n札幌落函館又搭返上去 望到都覺得無謂<br />\n夜晚行地獄谷一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排啲北海道行程post都好有趣<br />\n上星期先連續兩條友去10日想函館玩到去網走"},{"pid":"d4da02aa6fa1d40ffec039c09dd0e4b620b8ba89","tid":421801,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"不如函館下次先去啦<br />\n搭8個鐘車來回玩得1日真係有D無謂"},{"pid":"fa4dc683c270993ca21475491560df69c912542f","tid":421801,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"得罪講句你咁既plan去到最後只會全日係架車度<br />\n係我就一日最多去三個景點算鳩數"},{"pid":"d084ac183297a54af32f1cc44511702dd183a94a","tid":421801,"uid":53660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"典形香港人既瘋狂行程<br />\n見到都攰"},{"pid":"6a04c0e1c0085e720d05eaeea16a3a49ca60c6b8","tid":421801,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"我十三日都未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時節去網走果邊唔值得 冇破冰船<br />\n等四月啦 旭川可以去埋美瑛"},{"pid":"1f524294b096a33717c12cf9f8f7623bd1ef382e","tid":421801,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>典形香港人既瘋狂行程<br />\n見到都攰</blockquote><br />\n岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去北海道都咁rushy"},{"pid":"821a173137ba3cf4808ec886afb4962ed64bf3ab","tid":421801,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>典形香港人既瘋狂行程<br />\n見到都攰</blockquote><br />\n岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去北海道都咁rushy</blockquote><br />\n上次去函館咩都慢到仆街<br />\n搞到成個人都變慢埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}